Rank Group May Buy Casinos From Gala Coral, Mail on Sunday Says

-- B y   K e i t h   J e n k i n s
-- 
2011-06-12T12:28:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-12/rank-group-may-buy-casinos-from-gala-coral-mail-on-sunday-says.html
Rank Group Plc (RNK)  may make a takeover
bid for rival Gala Coral’s casino business, the Mail on Sunday
reported, without citing anyone.  The purchase would cement Maidenhead, England-based Rank as
Britain’s biggest casino operator, the Mail said. Gala’s casino
business is valued at as much as 300 million pounds ($487
million), according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Keith Jenkins in London at 
 kjenkins3@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dick Schumacher at 
 dschumacher@bloomberg.net . 